query:
SELECT 
  SUBSTRING(id_paciente, 1, 7) as prefixo,
  COUNT(*) as total,
  MIN(created_at) as primeiro_criado,
  MAX(created_at) as ultimo_criado
FROM pacientes 
WHERE tenant_id = 1 
  AND id_paciente NOT LIKE 'MIG-%'
GROUP BY SUBSTRING(id_paciente, 1, 7)
ORDER BY total DESC
LIMIT 20;
